hadiths[29]{hadithnumber,text}:
1146,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala ney razaat (doodh pilaane) sey bhi wo sarey rishtey haram kar diye hain jo nasab sey haram hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , ibne-Abbas aur Umme-Habiba (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. is silsiley mein hum unkey darmiyan is barey mein koi ikhtilaf nahin jantey."
1147,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah ney raza'at (doodh pilaane) sey bhi wo tamam rishtey haram qarar dey diye hain jo wiladat (nasab) sey haram hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. hamein nahin malum ke unke darmiyan is barey mein koi ikhtilaf hai.
1148,"merey razaai (doodh shareek) chacha aaye , wo mujh sey andar aaney ki ijazat mang rahey they, to mainey unhen ijazat deney sey inkar kiya yahan tak ke main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ijazat ley lun , to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''wo terey paas aa saktey hain kyonkey wo terey chacha hain.''  is par unhoney arz kiya : mujhey aurat ney doodh pilaya hai, mard ney nahin, to aap ney farmaya : ''terey chacha hain, wo terey paas aa saktey hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai unhoney « لبن فحل » (mard ke doodh) ko haram kaha hai. is baab mein asal Aaisha ki hadees hai. 3- aur baaz ehle-ilm ney «لبن فحل » (mard ke doodh) ki rukhsat (chhoot) di hai. pehla qol ziyada sahih hai."
1149,"Un sey eik aisey shakhs ke barey mein puchha gaya jis key paas do londiyan hon, un mein sey eik ney eik ladki ko doodh pilaya hai aur dusri ney eik ladkey ko. to kya us ladkey key liye jayez hai ke wo us ladki sey shaadi karey. unhoney (ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma) ney kaha : nahin. isliye ke «لقاح» eik hi hai padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : yehi is baab mein asal hai. Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi isi key qaail hain."
1150,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''eik baar ya do baar chhaati sey doodh choos leney sey hurmate-raza'at (doodh ki hurmat) Sabit nahin hoti.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Umme Fazal , Abu-Hurera , Zuber bin Awam aur ibne Zuber (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- is hadees ko deegar kaee logon ney ba-tareeq : (Hisham bin Urwaa an Abeeh an Abdullah bin Zuber an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat kiya hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''eik ya do baar doodh choos leney sey doodh ki hurmat Sabit nahin hoti.'' aur Muhammad bin Dinar ney ba-tareeq : (Hisham bin Urwaa an Abeeh an Abdullah bin Zuber an Zubair an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat kya hai, is mein Muhammad bin Dinar Basraa ney Zuber key wastey ka izafa kiya hai. lekin ye ghair mehfooz hai. 4- muhaddeseen key nazdik sahih ibne-Abi Muleka ki riwayat hai jisey unhoney ba-tareeq : (Abdullah bin Zubair an Aaysha an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat kiya hai. 5- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : sahih ibne Zuber ki riwayat hai jisey unhoney Aaisha sey riwayat ki hai aur Muhammad bin Dinar ki riwayat jis mein : Zuber key wastey ka izafa hai wo darasal Hisham bin Urwa sey marvi hai jisey unhoney apney walid Urwa sey aur unhoney Zuber sey riwayat ki hai. 6- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. 7- Aaisha kehti hain ke Quran mein (pehley  das razaa'at wali aayat nazil ki gaee phir is mein sey paanch mansookh kar di gaeen to paanch razaa'aten baqi reh gaeen, aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat hui to maamla inhen paanch par qaaim raha. 8- aur Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) aur baaz dusri paak biwiyan (Raziallahu Anhuma) isi ka fatwa deti thin, aur yehi Shafai aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. 9- Imam Ahmed Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadees ''eik baar ya do baar ke choosney sey hurmat sabit nahin hoti'' ke qaail hain aur unhoney ye bhi kaha hai ke agar koi Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key paanch razaa'at waley qol ki taraf jaey to ye qawi mazhab hai. lekin unhen iska fatwa deney ki himmat nahin hui. 10- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke razaat (doodh pilana) thodi ho ya ziyada jab pet tak pahunch jaey to us sey hurmat sabit ho jati hai. yehi Sufiyan Sory , Malik bin Anas , Auzaai , Abdullah bin Mubarak , Wakee aur ehle-Koofa ka qol hai."
1151,"Mainey eik aurat sey shaadi ki to eik kaali kaluti aurat ney hamarey paas aa kar kaha : mainey tum dono ko doodh pilaya hai, mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar arz kiya ke mainey falan ki beti falan sey shaadi ki hai, ab eik kaali kaluti aurat ney aa kar kaha ke mainey tum dono ko doodh pilaya hai, wo jhoot keh rahi hai. aap ney apna chehra mujh sey pher liya to main aap key chehrey ki taraf sey aaya , aap ney ( phir ( apna chehra pher liya. mainey arz kiya : wo jhooti hai. aap ney farmaya : ''ye kaisey ho sakta hai jabke wo keh chuki hai ke usney tum dono ko doodh pilaya hai. apni biwi apney sey alehda kar do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aqba bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is hadees ko kaee aur bhi logon ney ibne-Abi Muleka sey riwayat kiya hai aur ibne-Abi Muleka ney Aqba bin Haris sey riwayat ki hai aur un logon ney is mein Ubaid bin abi Maryam key wastey ka zikr nahin kiya hai, neez (isi ke saath) is mein « دعها عنك » ''usey apney sey alehda kar do''  ka zikr bhi nahin hai. is baab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai. unhoney razaat (doodh pilane) key silsiley main eik aurat ki shahadat ko durust qarar diya hai. 4- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : raza'at (doodh pilane) key silsiley main eik aurat ki shahadat jayez hai. lekin us sey qism bhi li jaeygi. Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya isi key qaail hain. 5- aur baaz ehle-ilm ney kaha hai ke eik aurat ki gawahi durust nahin jab tak ke wo eik sey zayed na hon. ye Shafai ka qol hai. 6- Wakee kehtey hain : eik aurat ki gawahi faisley mein durust nahin. aur agar eik aurat ki gawahi sun kar wo biwi sey alehdgi ikhtiyar kar ley to ye aen taqwa hai."
1152,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' raza'at (doodh pilane) sey hurmat usi waqt sabit hoti hai jab wo antdiyon ko phaad dey, aur ye doodh chudaney sey pehley ho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke razaat ki hurmat us waqt hoti hai jab bachchey ki umr do baras sey kam ho, aur jo do baras purey honey key baad ho to us sey koi chiz haram nahin hoti."
1153,"Unhoney Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha ke Allah key Rasool ! mujh sey raza'at (doodh pilane) ka haq kis chiz sey ada hoga? aap ney farmaya : ''eik jaan : ghulam ya laundi key zariey sey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isi tarah isey Yahya bin Saeed Qataan , Hatim bin Ismail aur kaee logon ney ba-tareeq : (Hisham bin Urwaa an Abeeh an Hujjaaj bin Hujjaaj an Abeeh an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai. aur Sufiyan bin Uena ney ba-tareeq : (Hisham bin Urwaa an Abeeh an Hujjaaj bin abi Hujjaaj an Abeeh an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai aur ibne Uena ki hadees ghair mehfooz hai. sahih wohi hai jisey un logon ney Hisham bin Urwa sey aur unhoney apney walid sey riwayat ki hai. (yani : (Hujjaaj bin Hujjaaj) wali na ke (Hujjaaj bin abi Hujjaaj) wali) 3- aur « مايذهب عني مذمة الرضاعة » sey murad raza'at (doodh pilane) ka haq aur uska zimma hai. wo kehtey hain : jab tum doodh pilaney wali ko eik ghulam dey do , ya eik laundi to tum ney uska haq ada kar diya. 4- abu-Tufel (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki gaee hai, wo kehtey hain ke main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath betha huwa tha. itney main eik aurat aai to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apni chadar bichha di, yahan tak ke wo is par beth gaee, jab wo chali gaee to kaha gaya : yehi wo aurat thi jisney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko doodh pilaya tha."
1154,"Bareera key shohar ghulam they, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Barira ko ikhtiyar diya, to unhoney khud ko ikhtiyar kiya, (Urwa kehtey hain) agar Barira ke shohar azad hotey to aap Barira ko ikhtiyar na detey."
1155,"Bareera key shohar azad they, phir bhi Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen ikhtiyar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isi tarah Hisham ney apney walid Urwa sey aur Urwa ney Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey riwayat ki hai, wo kehti hain ke Barira ka shohar ghulam tha. 3- Ikrima sey riwayat hai ke ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : mainey Bareera key shohar ko dekha hai, wo ghulam they aur unhen Mughees kaha jata tha. 4- isi tarah ki ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat ki gaee hai. 5- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo kehtey hain ke jab laundi azad mard key nikah mein ho aur wo azad kar di jaey to usey ikhtiyar nahin hoga. usey ikhtiyar sirf us surat mein hoga, jab wo azad ki jaey aur wo kisi ghulam ki zojiyat mein ho. yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. 6- lekin Aamash ney ba-tareeq : ( إبراهيم an الأسود an عائشة) riwayat ki hai ke Barira key shohar azad they to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen ikhtiyar diya. aur Abu Awaana ney bhi is hadees ko ba-tareeq : (الأعمش an إبراهيم an الأسود an عائشة) Bareera ke qisse ke silsiley mein riwayat kiya hai, Aswad kehtey hain : Barira key shohar azad they. 7- Tabe-een aur unkey baad key logon mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. aur yehi Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-Koofa ka bhi qol hai."
1156,"Bareera key shohar bani Mughira key eik kalay kalutey ghulam they, jis din Bareera azad ki gaeen, Allah ki qasam, goya main unhen Madiney ke gali-kunchon aur kinaron mein apney samney dekh raha hun ke unkey aansu un ki daadhi par beh rahey hain, wo unhen mana rahey hain ke wo unhen sath mein rehney ke liye chun lein lekin unhoney aisa nahin kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1157,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''bachcha sahibe-firaash (yani Shohar ya Malik) ka hoga padhi. aur zaani key liye patthar hongey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein umr , Usman , Aaisha , abu-Umama , Amr bin Khaarija , Abdullah bin umr , Bara bin Aazib aur Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
1158,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik aurat ko dekha to aap Zenab (Raziallahu Anha) key paas tashrif laye aur aap ney apni zarurat puri ki aur bahar tashrif la kar farmaya : ''aurat jab samney aati hai to wo shetan ki shakal mein aati hai, lihaza jab tum mein sey koi kisi aurat ko dekhey aur wo usey bhali lagey to apni biwi key paas aaye isliye ke uskey paas bhi usi jaisi chiz hai jo uskey paas hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir ki hadees sahih Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- Hisham Dustwaai darasal Hisham bin Sanbar hain."
1159,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' agar main kisi ko kisi key liye sajda karney ka hukm deta to main aurat ko hukm deta ke wo apney shohar ko sajda karey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Muaz bin Jabal , Suraqa bin Malik bin Jasham , Aaisha , ibne-Abbas , Abdullah bin abi Aufi , Talaq bin Ali , Umme-Salma , Anas aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1160,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab aadmi apni biwi ko apni khahish puri karney key liye bulaey to usey fauran aana chahiye agar-che wo tanur par ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
1161,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo aurat mar jaey aur uska shohar us sey khush ho to wo jannat mein dakhil hogi ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
1162,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' eman mein sab sey kamil momin wo hai jo sab sey behtar akhlaq wala ho, aur tum mein sab sey behtar wo hai jo akhlaq main apni aurton key haq mein sab sey behtar ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1163,"mujh sey merey walid ney bayan kya ke wo hajjatul-wadaa mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath shareek huye . aap ney Allah ki hamd o sanaa bayan ki. aur) logon ko) nasihat ki aur unhen samjhaya . phir Raavi ney is hadees main eik qissa ka zikr kya is mein ye bhi hai ke aap ney farmaya : '' suno ! aurton key sath khair-khahi karo . isliye ke wo tumharey paas qaidi hain. tum us ( ham-bistari aur apni ismat aur apney maal ki amanat waghera) key ilawa aur kuch ikhtiyar nahin rakhtey (aur jab wo apna farz ada karti hon to phir unkey sath bad-suluki ka jawaz kya hai) haan agar wo kisi khuli hui be-hayai ka irtikab karen (to phir tumhen unhen saza deney ka hai) pas agar wo aisa karen to unhen bistaron sey alag chhod do aur unhen maaro lekin aziyat naak maar na ho, uskey baad agar wo tumhari mutee ho jaeyn to phir unhen saza deney ka koi aur bahana na talash karo, suno ! jis tarah tumhara tumhari biwiyon par haq hai isi tarah tum par tumhari biwiyon ka bhi haq hai. tumhara haq tumhari biwiyon par ye hai ke wo tumharey bistar par aisey logon ko na raundney den jinhen tum napasand kartey ho, aur tumharey ghar mein aisey logon ko aaney ki ijazat na den jinhen tum achcha nahin samajhtey. suno ! aur tum par unka haq ye hai ke tum unkey libas aur pehney mein achcha sulook karo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. - « عوان عندكم » ka maana hai tumharey haathon mein qaidi hain."
1164,"eik eraab ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar kaha : Allah key Rasool ! hum main eik shakhs sehra ( biyaabaan ( mein hota hai, aur us ko hawa khaarij ho jati hai (aur wuzu toot jata hai) aur pani ki qillat bhi hoti hai (to wo kya karey ? ( Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum mein sey kisi ki jab huwa khaarij ho jaey to chaahiye ke wo wuzu karey , aur aurton ki peeth mein sohbat na karo, Allah Taala haq baat sey nahin sharmata ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali bin Talaq ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- aur mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke siwaye is eik hadees key Ali bin Talaq ki koi aur hadees mujhey nahin malum , jisey unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki ho, aur Talaq bin Ali Sahimi ki riwayat sey main ye hadees nahin janta . goya un ki raey ye hai ke ye Sahaba mein sey koi aur aadmi hain, padhi. 3- is bab mein umr , Khuzaima bin Sabit , ibne-Abbas aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1165,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah us shakhs ki taraf ( rehmat ki nazar sey) nahin dekhaga jo kisi mard ya kisi aurat ki peeth mein sohbat karey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
1166,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey koi hawa khaarij karey to chaahiye ke wuzu karey aur tum aurton ki peeth mein sohbat na karo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Ali sey murad Ali bin Talaq hain.
1167,"jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khaadima thin, wo kehti hain ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' apney shohar key ilawa gheron key samney banao singaar kar key itra kar chalney wali aurat ki misal qiyamat key din ki taariki ki tarah hai, uskey paas koi Noor nahin hoga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko hum sirf Musa bin Ubeda hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- Musa bin Ubeda apney hifz key talluq sey zaeef qarar diye jatey hain, wo Sadooq hain, un sey Shoba aur Sory ney bhi riwayat ki hai. 3- aur baaz ney isey Musa bin Ubeda sey riwayat kya hai, aur usey marfoo nahin kya hai."
1168,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah ko ghairat aati hai aur momin ko bhi ghairat aati hai, Allah ki ghairat is par hai ke momin koi aisa kaam karey jisey Allah ney is par haram kya hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- aur ye hadees Yahya bin abi Kasir (us tareeq sey bhi) sey marvi hai « an أبي سلمة an عروة an أسماء بنت أبي بكر an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم » ye dono hadisein sahih hain, 3- hujjaaj Sawaaf hi hujjaaj bin abi Usman hain. abu-Usman ka naam maisraa hai aur Hajjaaj ki kunniyat abu-Salat hai. Yahya bin Saeed ney unki toseeq ki hai. Yahya bin Saeed Qataan ney Hajjaaj sawaaf key barey mein kaha : wo Suqa zaheen aur hoshiyar hain, 4- is bab mein Aaisha aur Abdullah bin umr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1169,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kisi aurat key liye jo Allah aur youme-aakhirat par eman rakhti ho, halal nahin ke wo teen din padhi. ya us sey zayed ka safar karey aur uskey sath uska baap ya uska bhai ya uska shohar ya uska beta ya uska koi Mohrim na ho '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , ibne-Abbas aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi hai ke aap ney farmaya : '' aurat eik din aur eik raat ki masafat ka safar kisi Mohrim key baghair na kerey. ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo aurat key liye durust nahin samajhtey ke Mohrim key baghair safar kerey. ehle-ilm ka us aurat key barey mein ikhtilaf hai ke jo Haj ki istataat rakhti ho lekin uska koi Mohrim na ho to wo Haj karey ya nahin? baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain is par Haj nahin hai, isliye ke Mohrim bhi Allah Taala key irshad  من استطاع إليه سبيلا mein istataat sabeel mein dakhil hai. wo kehtey hain ke jab uska koi Mohrim na ho to wo istataat sabeel nahin rakhti . ye Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-koofa ka qol hai. aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke jab raasta maamoon ho, to wo logon key sath Haj mein ja sakti hai. yehi Malik aur Shafai ka bhi qol hai."
1170,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' koi aurat eik din aur eik raat ki masafat ka safar Mohrim key baghair na karey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1171,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' aurton key paas khilwat ( tanhai ( mein aaney sey bacho '' , is par ansaar key eik shakhs ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! dewar ( shohar key bhai ( key barey mein kya khayal hai? aap ney farmaya : '' dewar maut hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr , Jabir aur Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- aurton key paas khilwat ( tanhai ( mein aaney ki hurmat ka matlab wohi hai jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hai ke aap ney farmaya : '' koi shakhs kisi aurat key sath khilwat ( tanhai ( mein hota hai to uska teesra shetan hota hai'' , 4- « hamu» shohar key bhai yani dewar ko kehtey hain, goya aap ney dewar key bhawaj key sath tanhai mein honey ko haram qarar diya hai."
1172,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum log aisi aurton key gharon mein dakhil na ho, jinkey shohar gharon par na hon , isliye ke shetan tum mein sey har eik key andar aisey hi daudta hai jaisey khoon jism mein daudta hai'' , hamney arz kya : aap key bhi ? aap ney farmaya : '' haan merey bhi, lekin Allah Taala ney uskey muqabley mein meri madad ki hai, isliye mein) uskey shar sey) mehfooz rehta hun ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai. baaz logon ney Majaalid bin Saeed key hifz key talluq sey kalam kya hai, 1- Sufiyan bin Uena Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key qol « ولكن الله اعانني عليه فاسلم » '' lekin Allah ney meri madad ki hai isliye mein mehfooz rehta hun '' ki tashreeh mein kehtey hain : is sey murad ye hai ke ''main us shetan sey mehfooz rehta hun '' , na ye ke wo Islam ley aaya hai) kyonkey ( : shetan musalman nahin hota, 2- «ولاتلجوا على المغيبات» mein « مغیبة » sey murad wo aurat hai, jis ka shohar mojud na ho, « مغيبات » , padhi. « مغيبة » ki jama hai."
1173,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aurat ( sarapa ( parda hai, jab wo bahar nikalti hai to shetan us ko taakta hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
1174,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo aurat bhi apney shohar ko duniya mein takleef pahunchati hai to ( jannat ki) badi aakhon wali hooron mein sey uski biwi kehti hai : to usey takleef na dey . Allah tujhey halak karey , ye to wesay bhi terey paas bas musafir hai, qarib hai ke ye tujhey chhod kar hamarey paas aa jaey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi tareeq sey jantey hain, 2- Ismail bin Ayash ki riwaayatein jinhen unhoney ehal Sham sey riwayat ki hain behtar hai, lekin ehal hijaaz aur ehal iraaq sey un ki riwaayatein munkar hain."
